&lt;p>Happy Terror/Treat day! This is for my wife whom I&amp;rsquo;m missing very much while she&amp;rsquo;s away for work. This image is inspired by her love of scary fun-things as well as her love of our little ham-star, Misha. I hope you Enjoy!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Melech - Warlock Character Concept</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/melech-warlock-character-concept/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/melech-warlock-character-concept/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/marcus_melechwarlock_master.png" alt="Marcus_MelechWarlock_Master">
A friend of mine requested a concept image of his D&amp;amp;D character, Melech.  I agreed, and here we have the result.  I don&amp;rsquo;t feel like I did the character character the justice it deserves.It&amp;rsquo;s been awhile since I had done work like this, and so I could feel the rust hindering the piece.  In the future I will definitely have to do more work like this to keep my concept crafting well oiled.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>